Respect eslint rules when you generate code.

For .astro files, execute `npx eslint --print-config src/pages/index.astro` and comply with the output.
For .mdx files, execute `npx eslint --print-config src/content/home.mdx` and comply with the output.
For .js and .ts files, execute `npx eslint --print-config eslint.config.js` and comply with the output.